322
00:24:12.960 --> 00:24:15.879
There's nothing to suggest
he knows anything about this case.

323
00:24:15.880 --> 00:24:18.199
Yes. but he just might
help shed light on -

324
00:24:18.200 --> 00:24:20.799
Have you done a record-check
