348
00:26:25.640 --> 00:26:28.479
- Just go home. Ellis.
- You can't
tell me they're not connected.

349
00:26:28.480 --> 00:26:31.759
You need to stop playing at being
detective. For your own sake. right?

350
00:26:31.760 --> 00:26:35.239
- Fuck off.
- For your own sake. You're
fucking high risk and you know it.

351
00:26:35.240 --> 00:26:37.319
You know everyone here.
you're impulsive.

352
00:26:37.320 --> 00:26:39.719
