401
00:32:30.520 --> 00:32:33.119
He was that upset.
Shell. I understand.

402
00:32:33.120 --> 00:32:35.159
I'm so sorry -
I should be furious with you.

403
00:32:35.160 --> 00:32:37.000
Do you know. I am furious with you.

404
00:32:39.400 --> 00:32:43.759
I didn't tell Danny but I saw you
at Spider Island with Kieran.

405
00:32:43.760 --> 00:32:47.199
You're such a fucking nosey parker.
Jackie Ellis.

406
00:32:47.200 --> 00:32:49.479
This has nothing to do with Kieran.

407
00:32:49.480 --> 00:32:51.399
Not in the way you think.

408
00:32:51.400 --> 00:32:54.599
Well. in what way then?
Stay out of this.

409
00:32:54.600 --> 00:32:58.000
Are you still seeing him?
It was a bloody long time ago.

410
00:33:02.760 --> 00:33:04.799
Just leave it. yeah?

411
00:33:04.800 --> 00:33:07.800
Wasn't it around the time
Cefin was born. Shell?

412
00:33:12.240 --> 00:33:14.200
Stay out of it.

413
00:33:37.640 --> 00:33:39.440
(EXHALES SHAKILY)

414
00:33:51.400 --> 00:33:53.160
What you doing here?

415
00:33:56.040 --> 00:34:00.359
- I couldn't sleep.
- What about my
sister? Get yourself home.

416
00:34:00.360 --> 00:34:03.400
Be with her and the boys.
What do you think you're doing?

417
00:34:04.240 --> 00:34:08.640
- She's alright.
- She's bloody not.
Now. go home. Now.

418
00:35:07.760 --> 00:35:10.480
The hair we found on his body
is not Cefin's.

419
00:35:11.200 --> 00:35:13.440
We ran it through the database.
no match.

420
00:35:14.320 --> 00:35:15.880
OK.

421
00:35:17.080 --> 00:35:20.839
Any other details?
Er. it's cut short. Brownish.

422
00:35:20.840 --> 00:35:22.639
Right.

423
00:35:22.640 --> 00:35:26.039
The fingernail scrapings...
Yeah... contain butyl rubber fibres

424
00:35:26.040 --> 00:35:29.240
and high-density
polyethylene fibres. No DNA.

425
00:35:30.160 --> 00:35:33.319
Likely your killer wore a
protective suit and rubber gloves.

426
00:35:33.320 --> 00:35:35.599
And we're not talking
about Marigolds.

427
00:35:35.600 --> 00:35:38.440
My killer?
- Most certainly.
- Shit.

428
00:35:39.360 --> 00:35:41.480
Cefin was held under the water...

429
00:35:42.800 --> 00:35:45.159
...and he struggled.

430
00:35:45.160 --> 00:35:47.559
There's bruising
on the back of his neck.

431
00:35:47.560 --> 00:35:49.560
Finger marks.

432
00:35:55.880 --> 00:35:57.919
Shall I go on?

433
00:35:57.920 --> 00:35:59.840
Yeah. Yeah.

434
00:36:01.120 --> 00:36:04.919
Er. we found traces
of sodium hydroxide in Cefin's eyes.

435
00:36:04.920 --> 00:36:07.799
Sorry. sodium what?
Lye. Caustic soda.

436
00:36:07.800 --> 00:36:11.720
It's highly alkaline and corrosive.
depending on the dilution.

437
00:36:12.720 --> 00:36:15.919
Given the inflammation
around his eyes. nose and mouth.

438
00:36:15.920 --> 00:36:18.719
it appears to have been
in the water he was drowned in.

439
00:36:18.720 --> 00:36:20.759
But how would it have
ended up in the water?

440
00:36:20.760 --> 00:36:22.799
Are there any landfills
in that area?

441
00:36:22.800 --> 00:36:25.359
Landfills?
- First place I'd look.
- OK.

442
00:36:25.360 --> 00:36:27.079
Alright then.

443
00:36:27.080 --> 00:36:29.919
Look. is there er... anything
else I should know?

444
00:36:29.920 --> 00:36:32.079
Close contact with sodium hydroxide

445
00:36:32.080 --> 00:36:34.359
